log_loshours = ggplot(data = visit_data, aes(x = log(loshours))) +
  geom_histogram() 

log_losdays2 = ggplot(data = visit_data, aes(x = log(losdays2))) +
  geom_histogram()

log_mews = ggplot(data = visit_data, aes(x = log(mews))) +
  geom_histogram()

ggarrange(log_loshours, log_losdays2, log_mews + rremove("x.text"), 
          labels = c("A", "B", "C"),
          ncol = 3, nrow = 1)
